<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THIANG THLARAU LAM HMUHSAKTU CH175</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Thiang Thlarau lamhmuh-saktu, Khrihfa pawngah um zungzal, Kan kut in
 nifa hruai tuah, Vancung khua kan kai lioah, Thawngtha bik kan theih
 tikah, Retheimi an tha a nuam, &quot;Na lam kha kan hmuhsak lai, Zul tuah,&quot;
 bia nem in a ti.

[V2]
 Keimah he um ti ka hawi, Keimah bawmtu ka Khamhbawi, Khuamui ah
 kanchia ta hlah, Thinphannak kan huah tikah, Thlitu hrang ruahpi sur i,
 Kan ruahchannak lung a dong, &quot;Na lam kha kan hmuhsak lai, Zul tuah,&quot; bia
 nem in a ti.

[V3]
 Riantuannak a dih tikah, Pathian auhnak thawng ngai tuah, Ruahchannak
 in thla kan cam, Kan min tial cang kha kan hngalh, Thihnak tiva tan
 tikah, Jesuh thi hngatchan ca ah, &quot;Na lam kha kan hmuhsak lai, Zul tuah,&quot;
 bianem in a ti.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<hymn_number>175</hymn_number>
</song>